title: titanic CSH fan edit.avi
description:
fan edit of the movie titanic i created. I changed the story, and i used 102 songs over 2hr 44mins to lift the intensity of the scenes. It took me a month to make, and is one of my favorite films so messing around with it took a lot of consideration.

If you like good music, and you are a fan of one of the best disaster / love stories ever told then give my fan edit a try.
